'''Bahçelerde Menekşe Uy Gelin''' is a Turkish folkloric tune ([[Kaşık Havası]]).Bahçelerde Menekşe Uy Gelin is a form of the Turkish folkloric tune [[Kaşık Havası]].The meter is {{music|time|4|4}}.There are similar folkloric tunes known as ''[[Dam Başında Oturur]]''.

